snippet.title: Amber Reid is her Serious Medical Diagnosis Real or Fabricated - Body Language
snippet.description:
This video is based on Amber Reid a young woman who has a reputation for not always being forthcoming or truthful about her weight loss journey. But here I look at her video and analyze her body language. I check for her tells in regard to a serious medical diagnosis. 

This video is used in fair use and is a commentary of topical issues.
